data.description: Welcome! When you pull up, you are immediately in awe of the stunning view of the Rappahannock River located right behind this gorgeous brick front home. Walk through the front doors and you are greeted with hardwood flooring and BRAND NEW carpet. You enter into the formal living room which is open, airy and provides so much natural light! Just beyond the living room is a large sunroom with ample space to unwind as you take in the views! The main level also boasts two additional bedrooms with ample closet space and a large full bathroom with double vanities. In the rear of the home sits the primary bedroom, with the most amazing views and its own on suite full bathroom complete with a separate water closet! There is also access from the primary bedroom out into the sunroom. The kitchen offers ample cabinet and counter space. Off the kitchen sits a formal dining room, perfect for entertaining, a walk-in pantry which houses the laundry room and also provides access to the garage and another large family room. The basement is partially finished. The unfinished portion of the basement is massive and can easily hold two more bedrooms, with large windows looking out over the yard.
